# 🚀 Financial Document AI Assistant
## Strategy Performance Visualizations

![Equity Curve](./App_Image.png)

---
> AI-powered document intelligence system for querying and summarizing multiple PDFs with source attribution

---

## 📌 Overview

**MFinancial Document AI Assistant** is a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) application that enables users to upload documents and ask context-aware questions with precise source references.

Built to simulate real-world use cases such as:

* financial report analysis
* research document intelligence
* policy and compliance review

---

## ✨ Key Features

* 📄 Upload and process PDF documents
* 🔍 Context-aware question answering
* 🧠 Embedding-based semantic search (FAISS)
* 📑 Page-level source attribution
* 📝 Document summarization
* 💬 Chat history tracking
* ⚡ Fast local processing (except LLM call)

---

## 🧠 How It Works (RAG Pipeline)

User Question
↓
Embedding (Sentence Transformer)
↓
FAISS Vector Search
↓
Top Relevant Chunks Retrieved
↓
LLM (OpenAI) → Answer Generation
↓
Answer + Source Pages Returned

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

* **Frontend:** Streamlit
* **Embedding Model:** SentenceTransformers (MiniLM)
* **Vector Store:** FAISS
* **LLM:** OpenAI (GPT-4o-mini)
* **Processing:** Python

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* Python
* Streamlit
* PyPDF
* Sentence Transformers
* FAISS
* OpenAI API
* NumPy
* Python Dotenv

