## 🎯 Real-World Use Cases

* 📈 Financial Statement Analysis
* 🧾 Equity Research Reports
* 📚 Knowledge Base Search
* ⚖️ Legal Document Review
* 🏢 Internal Business Documents

---

## 🚧 Current Limitations

* Character-based chunking
* No table extraction yet
* No confidence scoring
* Limited summarization scope

---

## 🔮 Future Enhancements

* Multi-PDF support (in progress)
* Smart predefined questions
* Table extraction (Camelot / pdfplumber)
* Paragraph-based chunking
* Confidence scoring
* Financial-specific insights extraction

---

## 💡 Key Learning Outcomes

* Built end-to-end RAG pipeline
* Implemented vector search using FAISS
* Designed LLM prompt for grounded answers
* Managed document chunking and embeddings
* Created interactive UI using Streamlit

